      <title>Mysql主从搭建(Docker)</title>
      <link href="/2022/05/12/Mysql%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>/2022/05/12/Mysql%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1-准备-Mysql-配置文件-my-cnf"><a href="#1-准备-Mysql-配置文件-my-cnf" class="headerlink" title="1. 准备 Mysql 配置文件(my.cnf)"></a>1. 准备 Mysql 配置文件(my.cnf)</h3><blockquote><p>my.cnf 配置说明</p><ol><li><mark class="hl-label pink">default_authentication_plugin</mark> mysql8.0 引入了新特性 caching_sha2_password,这种密码加密方式 navicat 不支持,这里设置为 mysql_native_password</li><li><mark class="hl-label pink">server-id</mark> 在 mysql 集群中需要唯一</li><li><mark class="hl-label pink">read-only</mark> 1:表示该库只读/0:表示该库为读写 (默认 root 用户无视此规则,super-read-only 可以配置 root 的读写权限)</li><li><mark class="hl-label pink">binlog_format</mark>  二进制日志格式:<blockquote><ul><li><mark class="hl-label purple">ROW</mark>  : 记录一行数据的变更</li><li><mark class="hl-label purple">STATEMENT</mark>  : 记录数据操作的对应 Sql 语句</li><li><mark class="hl-label purple">MIXED</mark>  : ROW 和 STATEMENT 的混合(当 STATEMENT 有歧义时会转换为 ROW 格式)</li></ul></blockquote></li></ol></blockquote><div class="tabs" id=""><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#-1">master配置</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#-2">slave配置</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active" id="-1"><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[mysqld]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">character-set-server</span> = utf8</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># mysql8.0引入了新特性caching_sha2_password,这种密码加密方式navicat不支持,这里设置为mysql_native_password</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">default_authentication_plugin</span> = mysql_native_password</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#server-id 在mysql集群中需要唯一</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server-id</span> = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#read-only 1:表示该库只读/0:表示该库为读写</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">read-only</span> = <span class="number">0</span> <span class="comment">#master设置为读写</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#binlog_format 二进制日志的格式设置为ROW,记录每行的变化,分别有ROW/statement/mixed三种</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">binlog_format</span> = ROW</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#设置不需要同步的数据库</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">replicate-ignore-db</span>=mysql</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">replicate-ignore-db</span>=sys</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">replicate-ignore-db</span>=information_schema</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">replicate-ignore-db</span>=performance_schema</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">pid-file</span>        = /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.pid</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">socket</span>          = /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">datadir</span>         = /var/lib/mysql</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">secure-file-priv</span>= NULL</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="-2"><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[mysqld]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">character-set-server</span> = utf8</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># mysql8.0引入了新特性caching_sha2_password,这种密码加密方式navicat不支持,这里设置为mysql_native_password</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">default_authentication_plugin</span> = mysql_native_password</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#server-id 在mysql集群中需要唯一</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server-id</span> = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#read-only 1:表示该库只读/0:表示该库为读写</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">read-only</span> = <span class="number">1</span> <span class="comment">#slave设置为只读</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#binlog_format 二进制日志的格式设置为ROW,记录每行的变化,分别有ROW/statement/mixed三种</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">binlog_format</span> = ROW</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">pid-file</span>        = /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.pid</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">socket</span>          = /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">datadir</span>         = /var/lib/mysql</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">secure-file-priv</span>= NULL</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><h3 id="2-创建一个自定义-Docker-网络"><a href="#2-创建一个自定义-Docker-网络" class="headerlink" title="2.创建一个自定义 Docker 网络"></a>2.创建一个自定义 Docker 网络</h3><blockquote><p>因为 docker 容器的 ip 是变化的,自定义网络,可以为每个容器指定 IP,搭建主从的时候会方便一些<br>–driver bridge 使用桥接模式<br>–subnet 172.32.0.0&#x2F;16 表示子网 ip 可以分配 172.32.0.2 到 172.32.255.255<br>–gateway 172.32.0.1 网关<br>mysql-ms 自定义网络的名字</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker network create --driver bridge --subnet 172.32.0.0/16 --gateway 172.32.0.1 mysql-ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看创建的自定义网络详情"><a href="#查看创建的自定义网络详情" class="headerlink" title="查看创建的自定义网络详情"></a>查看创建的自定义网络详情</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker network inspect mysql-ms</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.maiscript.com/blog/mysqlMasterSlave/m-d-1.png"></p><h3 id="3-编写-docker-compose-yaml-文件"><a href="#3-编写-docker-compose-yaml-文件" class="headerlink" title="3.编写 docker-compose.yaml 文件"></a>3.编写 docker-compose.yaml 文件</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">version:</span> <span class="string">&quot;3.4&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">master:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">mysql:8.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="number">6380</span><span class="string">:3306</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">./conf/master/my.cnf:/etc/mysql/my.cnf</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">networks:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">mysql-ms:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ipv4_address:</span> <span class="number">172.32</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">environment:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD:</span> <span class="number">123456</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">slave:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">mysql:8.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">slave</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="number">6381</span><span class="string">:3306</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">./conf/slave/my.cnf:/etc/mysql/my.cnf</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">networks:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">mysql-ms:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ipv4_address:</span> <span class="number">172.32</span><span class="number">.0</span><span class="number">.3</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">environment:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD:</span> <span class="number">123456</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">networks:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">mysql-ms:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">external:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-执行-docker-compose-yaml-脚本-启动-master-和-salve-节点-mysql-容器"><a href="#4-执行-docker-compose-yaml-脚本-启动-master-和-salve-节点-mysql-容器" class="headerlink" title="4. 执行 docker-compose.yaml 脚本,启动 master 和 salve 节点 mysql 容器"></a>4. 执行 docker-compose.yaml 脚本,启动 master 和 salve 节点 mysql 容器</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-compose up</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-创建一个有主从复制权限的帐号"><a href="#5-创建一个有主从复制权限的帐号" class="headerlink" title="5. 创建一个有主从复制权限的帐号"></a>5. 创建一个有主从复制权限的帐号</h3><h4 id="1-执行命令进入-master-容器"><a href="#1-执行命令进入-master-容器" class="headerlink" title="1. 执行命令进入 master 容器"></a>1. 执行命令进入 master 容器</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">exec</span> -it master容器ID /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-创建帐号-并给于主从复制权限"><a href="#2-创建帐号-并给于主从复制权限" class="headerlink" title="2. 创建帐号,并给于主从复制权限"></a>2. 创建帐号,并给于主从复制权限</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql&gt; CREATE USER <span class="string">&#x27;master&#x27;</span>@<span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span> IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY <span class="string">&#x27;master@123456&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.02 sec)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mysql&gt; GRANT REPLICATION SLAVE ON *.* TO <span class="string">&#x27;master&#x27;</span>@<span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
